    "content": "<h2>Sunday Venture Studio Memo</h2><p>🎯 战略雷达 - 2026-04-21</p><p>独立Agent世界模型自发形成几何同构表示，实现互操作性 | 95/100 | Strategic Radar</p><p>🏷️ 标签：Long-horizon Agent / 世界模型 / 多Agent系统 / 数据飞轮</p><p>一句判断：\n独立Agent世界模型，自发形成几何同构表示。</p><p>为什么现在：\n揭示了独立Agent在学习世界模型时能自发形成可对齐的内部表示，是多Agent系统互操作性和数据飞轮的底层机制。</p><p>非共识视角：\n多数多Agent系统关注显式通信或共享模型，此研究发现独立Agent能自发形成“几何同构”的表示，为去中心化Agent协作提供了新的理论基础和技术路径。</p><p>破局点：\n发现独立学习世界模型的Agent，其内部表示空间存在近似线性等距关系，实现了表示的透明转换和学习加速，为去中心化Agent系统的互操作性和数据效率提供了突破性机制。</p><p>行动建议：\nAgent团队 / 立即研究Social-JEPA的机制和代码，评估其在多Agent协作、知识迁移和数据飞轮构建上的应用潜力 / 未来2个月内。</p><p>入选理由：\n发现独立学习世界模型的Agent能自发形成几何同构的内部表示，极大地简化了多Agent系统的互操作性和知识迁移，对Long-horizon Agent、世界模型和数据飞轮构建具有战略级影响。</p><h2>Source Context</h2><p>arXiv:2603.02263v2 Announce Type: replace-cross Abstract: World models compress rich sensory streams into compact latent codes that anticipate future observations. We let separate agents acquire such models from distinct viewpoints of the same environment without any parameter sharing or coordination. After training, their internal representations exhibit a striking emergent property: the two latent spaces are related by an approximate linear isometry, enabling transparent translation between them. This geometric consensus survives large viewpoint shifts and scant overlap in raw pixels. Leveraging the learned alignment, a classifier trained on one agent can be ported to the other with no additional gradient steps, while distillation-like migration accelerates later learning and markedly reduces total compute. The findings reveal that predictive learning objectives impose strong regulari...</p>",
