    "content": "<h2>Sunday Venture Studio Memo</h2><p>🎯 战略雷达 - 2026-04-21</p><p>Mind DeepResearch: 30B参数多Agent框架实现深度研究落地 | 92/100 | Strategic Radar</p><p>🏷️ 标签：Long-horizon Agent / 工程基础设施 / 非共识弱信号</p><p>一句判断：\n30B参数多Agent框架，高效完成深度研究并已落地。</p><p>为什么现在：\n证明中等规模模型通过精巧设计也能实现复杂Agent任务的领先性能，且有实际产品部署，具备极高参考价值。</p><p>非共识视角：\n业界普遍认为复杂Agent任务需要超大模型，但MindDR通过精细的三Agent协作架构和四阶段Agent专用训练管线，证明了30B参数模型也能实现领先性能，这为中小型团队开发高性能Agent提供了成本效益更高的路径。</p><p>破局点：\nMindDR通过“规划-深度搜索-报告”三Agent协作架构和SFT冷启动、Search-RL、Report-RL、偏好对齐四阶段训练管线，使30B参数模型在复杂深度研究任务上达到SOTA，并已在理想汽车部署，形成数据飞轮和商业壁垒。</p><p>行动建议：\n技术团队：立即研究MindDR的三Agent架构和四阶段训练管线，评估其在Sunday Venture Studio内部信息蒸馏和研究Agent中的复用性，本周内完成初步技术分析。投资团队：关注通过精巧Agent设计而非纯模型规模取胜的创业公司。</p><p>入选理由：\n典型的Long-horizon Agent成功案例，技术架构和训练方法有显著创新，且有明确的商业落地和数据飞轮潜力，战略相关度极高。</p><h2>Source Context</h2><p>arXiv:2604.14518v2 Announce Type: replace Abstract: We present Mind DeepResearch (MindDR), an efficient multi-agent deep research framework that achieves leading performance with only ~30B-parameter models through a meticulously designed data synthesis and multi-stage training pipeline. The core innovation of MindDR lies in a collaborative three-agent architecture (Planning Agent, DeepSearch Agent, and Report Agent) and a four-stage agent-specialized training pipeline comprising SFT cold-start, Search-RL, Report-RL and preference alignment. With this regime, MindDR demonstrates competitive performance even with ~30B-scale models. Specifically, MindDR achieves 45.7% on BrowseComp-ZH, 42.8% on BrowseComp, 46.5% on WideSearch, 75.0% on xbench-DS, and 52.5 on DeepResearch Bench, outperforming comparable-scale open-source agent systems and rivaling larger-scale models. MindDR has been deploy...</p>",
