    "content": "<h2>Sunday Venture Studio Memo</h2><p>🎯 战略雷达 - 2026-04-21</p><p>COEVO: LLM生成RTL代码，功能与PPA联合优化新范式 | 92/100 | Strategic Radar</p><p>🏷️ 标签：工程基础设施 / 模型与架构 / 非共识弱信号</p><p>一句判断：\nLLM生成芯片代码，同时优化功能和功耗性能面积。</p><p>为什么现在：\nLLM赋能芯片设计是硬科技前沿，COEVO解决了功能与PPA联合优化的核心难题。</p><p>非共识视角：\n传统LLM生成RTL代码方法通常先保证功能正确性再优化PPA，导致部分有潜力的设计被过早放弃。COEVO的“协同进化”框架，将正确性视为连续优化维度，允许部分正确但PPA优秀的方案参与迭代，这是一种更高效、更符合工程实践的优化范式。</p><p>破局点：\nCOEVO通过创新的协同进化框架，将功能正确性与PPA（功耗、性能、面积）优化统一，利用连续正确性维度、自适应正确性门和四维Pareto排序，显著提升了LLM生成RTL代码的质量，并在GPT-5.4-mini上超越所有Agent基线，为AI辅助芯片设计提供了关键突破。</p><p>行动建议：\n技术团队：立即研究COEVO的联合优化框架和评估方法，评估其在AI辅助硬件设计（如FPGA、ASIC）或复杂系统优化中的应用潜力，未来2周内完成初步技术分析。投资团队：关注AI赋能芯片设计/EDA领域的创业公司。</p><p>入选理由：\nLLM在芯片设计这一硬科技领域的重大突破，解决了多目标优化难题，具有极高的战略相关度和行动价值。</p><h2>Source Context</h2><p>arXiv:2604.15001v2 Announce Type: replace Abstract: LLM-based RTL code generation methods increasingly target both functional correctness and PPA quality, yet existing approaches universally decouple the two objectives, optimizing PPA only after correctness is fully achieved. Whether through sequential multi-agent pipelines, evolutionary search with binary correctness gates, or hierarchical reward dependencies, partially correct but architecturally promising candidates are systematically discarded. Moreover, existing methods reduce the multi-objective PPA space to a single scalar fitness, obscuring the trade-offs among area, delay, and power. To address these limitations, we propose COEVO, a co-evolutionary framework that unifies correctness and PPA optimization within a single evolutionary loop. COEVO formulates correctness as a continuous co-optimization dimension alongside area, dela...</p>",
