    "content": "<h2>Sunday Venture Studio Memo</h2><p>🎯 战略雷达 - 2026-04-21</p><p>SOAR：扩散模型自校正后训练，显著提升生成质量 | 92/100 | Strategic Radar</p><p>🏷️ 标签：模型与架构 / 非共识弱信号</p><p>一句判断：\n扩散模型自校正，生成图像更真实。</p><p>为什么现在：\n解决了扩散模型后训练中SFT的曝光偏差和RL的稀疏奖励问题，显著提升了生成模型的质量和鲁棒性。</p><p>非共识视角：\n多数扩散模型优化集中于SFT或RL，SOAR提出一种无奖励、密集监督的自校正方法，填补了两者之间的空白，其在提升模型泛化性和避免奖励欺骗上的优势被低估。</p><p>破局点：\nSOAR通过单次stop-gradient rollout和重噪，提供密集的每步监督，无需奖励模型，有效解决了曝光偏差和信用分配问题，可直接替代SFT作为更强的后训练阶段。</p><p>行动建议：\n研究团队：在未来2周内，研究SOAR方法，评估其在现有图像/视频生成模型训练中的应用潜力，并规划概念验证。</p><p>入选理由：\n该论文提出SOAR方法，通过自校正机制，在扩散模型后训练中提供密集、无奖励的每步监督，解决了SFT的曝光偏差和RL的稀疏奖励问题，显著提升生成质量。这直接影响模型与架构的训练方法和生成模型能力，是新训练方法，具有高行动可执行性。</p><h2>Source Context</h2><p>arXiv:2604.12617v2 Announce Type: replace-cross Abstract: The post-training pipeline for diffusion models currently has two stages: supervised fine-tuning (SFT) on curated data and reinforcement learning (RL) with reward models. A fundamental gap separates them. SFT optimizes the denoiser only on ground-truth states sampled from the forward noising process; once inference deviates from these ideal states, subsequent denoising relies on out-of-distribution generalization rather than learned correction, exhibiting the same exposure bias that afflicts autoregressive models, but accumulated along the denoising trajectory instead of the token sequence. RL can in principle address this mismatch, yet its terminal reward signal is sparse, suffers from credit-assignment difficulty, and risks reward hacking. We propose SOAR (Self-Correction for Optimal Alignment and Refinement), a bias-correction...</p>",
